## Compilation:

Under the cs488 directory do the following:

    $ cd A0
    $ premake4 gmake
    $ make

To run the program, type the command:

    $ ./A0

This program is tested on the VM.

---

##Manual: 

---

The scale factor is 0.1f, range is  0.5f to 3.0f.
Wall height scalse factor is 0.2f is from 0.0f to 3.0f
The persistence speed depends on drag speed.
